CHANGES for 3A-55

Started 05/05/00
------------------------------------------------
1. Added product version option -P to level_3_finalize_metadata.c



v1.6 ??/??/99  Packaged w/ gvs 4.13.
-------------------------------------------------
1. Added software version.
2. Created 3A55.h

v1.5
-------------------------------------------------
* Added more diagnosis messages in '3A-55'.
* Allows input filename to contain pathname.
* Fixed interrupt signal checking.
* Changed 3A-55 to execute in a tmp dir.
* Requires gv_utils v1.3
* Hardcoded some of the metadata fields: alg_id, data_id, alg_version, contact.
* Added the capability for uninstalling the software.

v1.4 (1/26/98) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.5
-------------------------------------------------
* Handles and creates empty granule product.

v1.3 (12/08/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.4
-------------------------------------------------
* Ported to HP-UX.
* Bug fixes in '3A-55'.

v1.2 (11/13/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.2
-------------------------------------------------
1. 3A-55 vertical profile TK_DEFAULT == vs = bug fix.
2. Requires gv_utils.


v1.1 (10/24/97) initially packaged w/ GVS v4.1
-------------------------------------------------
1. File management in 3A-55 keeps intermediate files
   and deletes metadata.bin on END.
2. Removed data center source from '3A55_metadata.txt'.
3. Fixed bugs related to metadata data. 

v1.0 (10/10/97) initially packaged w/ gvs pre-v4.1
-------------------------------------------------
Initially created.